OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A primary school has warned parents it 
OL,6, may have to close its doors because of 
OL,7, a worsening row over a pupil wearing a 
OL,8, Palestine flag patch to school.        
OL,10,FBarclay Primary School, in Leyton, east
OL,11,FLondon, said it may have to revert to  
OL,12,Fonline learning because of threats made
OL,13,Fagainst the school and its staff.      
OL,15,FGrowing anger at the school in December
OL,16,Fforced it to close early for Christmas.
OL,18,FThe pupil, whose mother is from Gaza,  
OL,19,Fhad been off school for weeks after    
OL,20,Frefusing to remove the patch.          
